nging-gender-easier/ | title = Catholic lobby group condemns Scottish government's plan to make legally changing gender easier | date = November 15, 2017 | accessdate = July 26, 2018 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Siker>Jeffrey Siker, ''Homosexuality and Religion''</ref>\n\n<ref name=Sherrington>{{cite news | url = http://www.catholicherald.co.uk/news/2017/11/17/bishop-sherrington-there-are-concerns-about-transgender-laws/ | title = Bishop Sherrington: 'There are concerns' about transgender laws in schools | publisher = Catholic Herald | first = Dan | last = Hitchens | date = November 17, 2017 | accessdate = July 26, 2018 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=slip>Slip op., pp. 2-3, ''Masterpiece Cakeshop, Ltd. v. Colorado Civil Rights Commission'', case no. 16-111, U.S. Supreme Court (June 4, 2018).</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"zenit.org\">{{cite web | title=Holy See on UN Declaration on Homosexuality | website=Zenit | date=December 18, 2008 | url=https://zenit.org/articles/holy-see-on-un-declaration-on-homosexuality/ | access-date=July 20, 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=zero>{{cite news | url = https://www.americamagazine.org/issue/zero-tolerance | title = Zero Tolerance: Why Catholics must condemn anti-gay violence | first = Carlos | last = Perez | date = November 25, 2014 | accessdate = July 26, 2018 | publisher = America magazine }}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==Works cited==\n*{{cite book|last=Peddicord|first=Richard |title=Gay and Lesbian Rights: A Question--sexual Ethics Or Social Justice?|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield|isbn=978-1-55612-759-5|year=1996 }}\n\n==Further reading==\n* {{cite web|url=https://www.br.de/nachrichten/kardinal-marx-homosexuelle-100.html|title=Erzbischof Reinhard Marx: \"Segnung homosexueller Paare ist m\u00f6glich\" - BR.de|first=Bayerischer|last=Rundfunk|date=3 February 2018|publisher=}}\n* [https://www.ndr.de/nachrichten/niedersachsen/Bischof-Bode-fuer-Segnung-von-Homo-Paaren,segnung100.html NDR.de: Bischof f\u00fcr Segnung von homosexuellen Paaren (German)], 10 January 2018\n* {{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/ni/2011/02/we_can_no_longer_keep_silent.html | title = We can no longer keep silent | first = William | last = Crawley | date = 18 February 2011 | accessdate =  | publisher = Will & Testament }}\n* {{cite web|url=http://www.spiegel.de/panorama/gesellschaft/reinhard-marx-kardinal-stellt-segnung-homosexueller-paare-in-aussicht-a-1191270.html|title=Katholische Kirche: Kardinal Marx stellt Segnung homosexueller Paare in Aussicht|date=3 February 2018|publisher=|via=Spiegel Online}}\n\n{{Religion and LGBT people|state=collapsed}}\n\n[[Category:Catholicism-related controversies]]\n[[Category:LGBT topics and Catholicism|Political activity]]\n[[Category:Catholicism and politics]]\n", "name_user": "Slugger O'Toole", "label": "safe", "comment": "Arranged references withscript", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Political_activity_of_the_Catholic_Church_on_LGBT_issues"}
